{"tid":2497212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜限定心事台 (135)","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T12:30:04.000Z","uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"72ba1cbda5b027ef1103a439b7eb2d5f871e13e2","tid":2497212,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:56:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong>許願樹!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希望M47快啲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老濛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙女需要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n?!?!都想要眼鏡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n王將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n木星要發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熊要熊啤啤同埋訓教唔好再俾人阻住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n村西透可以做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n正字GPA爆4同埋搵到女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腳腳繼續GPA爆4入UST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n料快啲有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWiedersehen識好多仔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夢要身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n春野可以同女神一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柴子考好ielts搭火箭去木星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙鹿搵到個正常既女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n范統可以順利入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCake要寧濫勿缺 搵到啱既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女生快高長大 學業進步 身體健康 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腦盧生日前岀pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (已實現)<br />\n寞人想睇到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">其實我諗我都係想身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老規矩<br />\n有心事又好無聊又好都可以放低係到<br />\n如果無見到無覆到麻煩提一提我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想有心事私下傾可以加我tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lingdong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flingdong&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=1f772987\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lingdong</a><br />\n所有野絕對保密<br />\n不過會覆得都好慢<br />\n有可能會過一兩日先覆你<br />\n因為我應該都係回post優先同有自己野要做<br />\n只要你放低我就會覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果太多人搵/我真係覆唔到可以搵木星<br />\n@threebridges"},{"pid":"310a5f9529aeda36b03f2ddc12b849199e0c40ff","tid":2497212,"uid":217283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"放工未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e271d6a829b0afc7eca02b6bec1c1bbcab6ccae4","tid":2497212,"uid":310818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbccfa3f4782376ecc32868d0e16a6f08f1eea0e","tid":2497212,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4cf525882a0f65499832670687ced594a3aaf4","tid":2497212,"uid":58416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" 